          <input semantic="NORMAL" source="#Cube-mesh-normals" offset="1"/>
          <input semantic="TEXCOORD" source="#Cube-mesh-map-0" offset="2" set="0"/>
          <p>7 0 0 2 0 1 3 0 2 5 1 3 6 1 4 7 1 5 3 2 6 0 2 7 1 2 8 1 3 9 4 3 10 5 3 11 7 4 12 6 4 13 2 4 14 5 5 15 4 5 16 6 5 17 3 6 18 2 6 19 0 6 20 1 7 21 0 7 22 4 7 23</p>
